                <note rend="inline" type="source">838.516/291: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Haiti</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Armour</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1934-05-26T13:00:00-04:00"
                            >May 26, 1934—1 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>37. Your 55, May 25, 2 p.m. We agree to insertion in article I of the treaty of
                    the phrase requested by the Haitian Government.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
